name: Gold Prime X SKR (TOMO)
info: Gold Prime X SKR is a digital asset backed by physical gold guarded and stored in the vaults of banks, entities and companies certified and guaranteed for the custody and reserve of assets.Characteristics: backup by certificate of deposit and SKR custody, digital gold linked to certificate of ownership, token of stable value that serves as a refuge of value, asset attached to the value of gold, little or no volatility and fluctuation,instant transactions, verification in seconds, each token represents absolute ownership of 1 troy ounce of gold (1ozt).
